values.description:
As part of the DIUx project we should contribute upstream some of the worlds that we have created. These models are quite big to host them in a git repository, some of the textures are above 90Mb.

Tully and I \(and I think Tully commented this with Nate\) that probably make sense to include this in  [http://models.gazebosim.org/](http://models.gazebosim.org/)

‌

Here some pictures about the worlds:

‌

![](data/bitbucket.org/repo/ReaGey7/images/395330769-baylands.jpg)
![](data/bitbucket.org/repo/ReaGey7/images/3050815312-ksql.jpg)
![](data/bitbucket.org/repo/ReaGey7/images/2651944201-mcmillan.jpg)
![](data/bitbucket.org/repo/ReaGey7/images/2143969525-sand_island.jpg)
![](data/bitbucket.org/repo/ReaGey7/images/2097319292-yosemite.jpg)
‌
